		<section id="flashcard">
			<title>Links to other flashcard programs</title>
			<p>The following list is a collection of links to other flashcard programs I am a aware of - and which I think are worth mentioning. Some of them have been an inspiration to <code>DingsBums?!</code>.</p>
			<p>If <code>DingsBums?!</code> cannot provide what you are looking for, try one of those. Or <a href="site:contact">tell me</a> what is missing, so I can improve the application!.</p>
			<ul>
				<li>The <a href="http://www.wikipedia.org">Wikipedia</a> entry for <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flashcard">flashcard</a> contains a lot of links to both programs and background material.</li>
